          <avActivityHighlights>In particular on steep sunny slopes there will be an increase in the danger of moist and wet avalanches.</avActivityHighlights>
          <avActivityComment>In particular on steep slopes small and medium-sized moist and wet avalanches are possible as a consequence of warming during the day and solar radiation. Slab avalanches are still possible.</avActivityComment>
          <snowpackStructureComment>The solar radiation will give rise to increasing moistening of the snowpack in all aspects. These conditions will cause a weakening of the snowpack. This applies in particular on steep sunny slopes. The surface of the snowpack will soften during the day.</snowpackStructureComment>
